h3cNS.name: h3cNS

revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

h3cNS.contactinfo: L3+ Team Huawei-3Com Technologies Co.,Ltd. Bing-jiang District Hangzhou P.R.China http://www.huawei-3com.com Zip:310053
h3cNS.description: This MIB contains objects to manage the configuration and status information of network traffic statistics. It classifies the IP packets by source IP address, source port, destination IP address, destination port, protocol, ToS and input interface, counts the octets and packets, and sends the statistic information to the specific collector.

h3cNSActiveTime.name: h3cNSActiveTime
h3cNSActiveTime.description: The stream will be aged when the active time of this stream exceeds this value. This object is in minute.

h3cNSInactiveTime.name: h3cNSInactiveTime
h3cNSInactiveTime.description: The stream will be aged when the inactive time of this stream exceeds this value. This object is in second.

h3cNSVersion.name: h3cNSVersion
h3cNSVersion.description: The version of the exported packet, which describes the format of the exported packet. It should export version 5 and version 8 when this object is 5, but it should export version 9 only when the value of this object is 9.

h3cNSAsType.name: h3cNSAsType
h3cNSAsType.description: The number of autonomous system (AS). This object can be origin or peer.

h3cNSTemplateRefreshRate.name: h3cNSTemplateRefreshRate
h3cNSTemplateRefreshRate.description: This object specifies the refresh rate in number of exported packets.

h3cNSTemplateTimeout.name: h3cNSTemplateTimeout
h3cNSTemplateTimeout.description: This object specifies the timeout rate in minutes.

h3cNSExportVlanOrIfIndex.name: h3cNSExportVlanOrIfIndex
h3cNSExportVlanOrIfIndex.description: This object describes the interface index at the exported packet. It can be interface index or vlan id according to the product.

h3cNSProcessSlotTable.name: h3cNSProcessSlotTable
h3cNSProcessSlotTable.description: This table describes the board which can enable network traffic statistics at the switch or router.

h3cNSProcessSlot.name: h3cNSProcessSlot
h3cNSProcessSlot.description: This object describes all boards which can processes network traffic statistics at the switch or router.

h3cNSExportConfigTable.name: h3cNSExportConfigTable
h3cNSExportConfigTable.description: This table describes the configuration of the exported packets.

h3cNSAggregationType.name: h3cNSAggregationType
h3cNSAggregationType.description: The aggregation type. v5Statistics type counts IP packets which have same source IP address, destination IP address, source port, destination port, protocol, ToS, input interface, output interface. AS type counts IP packets which have same source AS, destination AS, input interface and output interface. destinationPrefix type counts IP packets which have same destination AS, output interface, destination mask and destination prefix. sourcePrefix type counts IP packets which have same source AS, input interface, source mask and source prefix. protocolPort type counts IP packets which have same protocol, source port and destination port. prefix type counts IP packets which have same source AS, destination AS, input interface, output interface, source mask, source prefix, destination mask, destination prefix. tosAS type counts IP packets which have same tos, source AS, destination AS, input interface and output interface. tosDestinationPrefix type counts IP packets which have same tos, destination AS, output interface, destination mask and destination prefix. tosProtocolPort type counts IP packets which have same tos, protocol, source port and destination port. tosSourcePrefix type counts IP packets which have same tos, source AS, input interface, source mask and source prefix. tosPrefix type counts IP packets which have same tos, source AS, destination AS, input interface, output interface, source mask, source prefix, destination mask, destination prefix. prefixPort type counts IP packets which have same tos, input interface, output interface, source mask, source prefix, destination mask, destination prefix, source port and destination port.

h3cNSHostIPAddr.name: h3cNSHostIPAddr
h3cNSHostIPAddr.description: The destination IP address of the exported packet. This destination IP address is a NSC (NS Collector) address.

h3cNSHostPort.name: h3cNSHostPort
h3cNSHostPort.description: The destination port of the exported packets. This destination port is a NSC listening port.

h3cNSSrcIpAddr.name: h3cNSSrcIpAddr
h3cNSSrcIpAddr.description: The source IP address of the exported packets.

h3cNSState.name: h3cNSState
h3cNSState.description: The state of aggregation is enabled or disabled.

h3cNSExportInformationTable.name: h3cNSExportInformationTable
h3cNSExportInformationTable.description: This table describes the Information of the exported packets.

h3cNSExportType.name: h3cNSExportType
h3cNSExportType.description: This object is equal to h3cNSAggregationType.

h3cNSExportSlot.name: h3cNSExportSlot
h3cNSExportSlot.description: This object is equal to h3cNSProcessSlot.

h3cNSExportStream.name: h3cNSExportStream
h3cNSExportStream.description: This object counts the exported streams.

h3cNSExportNum.name: h3cNSExportNum
h3cNSExportNum.description: This object counts the exported packets.

h3cNSExportFail.name: h3cNSExportFail
h3cNSExportFail.description: This object counts the exported packets which failed to send. The error may be unreachable destination IP address.

h3cNSSourceSlot.name: h3cNSSourceSlot
h3cNSSourceSlot.description: The IP packet will be counted when it is passing through this slot.

h3cNSSourceIfIndex.name: h3cNSSourceIfIndex
h3cNSSourceIfIndex.description: The IP packet will be statistics when it through this interface. This object is equal to ifIndex at ifTable.

h3cNSDestSlot.name: h3cNSDestSlot
h3cNSDestSlot.description: This object is equal to h3cNSProcessSlot.

h3cNSDirect.name: h3cNSDirect
h3cNSDirect.description: This object describes which packets will be counted. It may be inbound or outbound packets through this interface.

h3cNSConfigRowStatus.name: h3cNSConfigRowStatus
h3cNSConfigRowStatus.description: SNMP Row Status Variable. Writable objects in the table may be written in any RowStatus state.

h3cNSStatusTable.name: h3cNSStatusTable
h3cNSStatusTable.description: This table describes current information of network traffic.

h3cNSSlot.name: h3cNSSlot
h3cNSSlot.description: This object is equal to h3cNSProcessSlot.

h3cNSActiveStreamNumber.name: h3cNSActiveStreamNumber
h3cNSActiveStreamNumber.description: This object counts current active streams.

h3cNSTotalStreamNumber.name: h3cNSTotalStreamNumber
h3cNSTotalStreamNumber.description: This object counts all statistic streams.

h3cNSTotalPacketNumber.name: h3cNSTotalPacketNumber
h3cNSTotalPacketNumber.description: This object counts all statistic packets.

h3cNSTotalOctetNumber.name: h3cNSTotalOctetNumber
h3cNSTotalOctetNumber.description: This object counts all statistic octets.

h3cNSMPLSActiveStreamNumber.name: h3cNSMPLSActiveStreamNumber
h3cNSMPLSActiveStreamNumber.description: This object counts current active MPLS streams.

h3cNSMPLSTotalStreamNumber.name: h3cNSMPLSTotalStreamNumber
h3cNSMPLSTotalStreamNumber.description: This object counts all statistic MPLS streams.

h3cNSMPLSTotalPacketNumber.name: h3cNSMPLSTotalPacketNumber
h3cNSMPLSTotalPacketNumber.description: This object counts all statistic MPLS packets.

h3cNSMPLSTotalOctetNumber.name: h3cNSMPLSTotalOctetNumber
h3cNSMPLSTotalOctetNumber.description: This object counts all statistic octets of MPLS packets.

h3cNSResetFlag.name: h3cNSResetFlag
h3cNSResetFlag.description: Reset all streams. The default value is disabled, and set this value to enabled when resetting.

h3cNSResetTime.name: h3cNSResetTime
h3cNSResetTime.description: The system up time when stream is reset.
